HEADWORD: Spiller
<hw>Spill"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who,
or that which, spills.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A kind of fishing line with many hooks; a
boulter.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

